name: BunnyHope “the peasant”
description: Our companion Bunny tried to be a landless peasant. Using basic farming tools, these poorly-dressed 3rd world traditional peasants works the land owned by the others (landlords) by renting with cash or trading the harvest.  Often times, they are the ones who suffers when the harvest fails or from fluctuation of their crops' value due to the illicit practice by the brokers (tengkulak in Indonesian) & market owners.
